**utf8regex** is a `GNU libc`_ `regex library`_ port, which does not use the
C-language `locale subsystem`_. Instead, UTF-8 encoding is used exclusively.

Both the interface_ and the implementation_ should closely follow the POSIX
specification.


.. _GNU libc:
   http://www.gnu.org/software/libc/

.. _regex library:
   http://www.gnu.org/software/libc/manual/html_node/Regular-Expressions.html

.. _locale subsystem:
   http://www.opengroup.org/onlinepubs/007908799/xsh/locale.h.html

.. _interface:
   http://www.opengroup.org/onlinepubs/007908799/xsh/regex.h.html

.. _implementation:
   http://www.opengroup.org/onlinepubs/007908799/xsh/regcomp.html

